</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/LibreOffice_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/LibreOffice_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "title": "LibreOffice \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664", "content_html": "<h1>LibreOffice \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664</h1>\n<h2>\u56fe\u6807\u6a21\u7cca</h2>\n<p>\u5728 <code>Tools | Options... | LibreOffice | View</code> \u4e2d, \u5c06 <code>Icon Theme</code> \u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e3a\u652f\u6301 SVG \u7684\u4e3b\u9898.</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Python_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Python_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "title": "Python \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664", "content_html": "<h1>Python \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664</h1>\n<h2>\u5b89\u88c5 pip</h2>\n<p>ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'pip'</p>\n<p><code>sh\ncurl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py\npython get-pip.py</code></p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Rust_%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Rust_%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91/", "title": "Rust \u5d4c\u5165\u5f0f\u5f00\u53d1", "content_html": "<h1>Rust \u5d4c\u5165\u5f0f\u5f00\u53d1</h1>\n<h2>STM32</h2>\n<h3>\u76ee\u6807</h3>\n<p>\u6dfb\u52a0\u5408\u9002\u7684\u76ee\u6807, \u4ee5 Cortex-M4(F) \u4e3a\u4f8b:</p>\n<p>```console\nrustup target add thumbv7em-none-eabi   # \u65e0\u6d6e\u70b9\u5904\u7406\u5355\u5143\nrustup target add thumbv7em-none-ea...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Thunderbird/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Thunderbird/", "title": "Thunderbird", "content_html": "<h1>Thunderbird</h1>\n<h2>\u6700\u5c0f\u5316\u5230\u6258\u76d8</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\u5728 <code>Settings | System Integration</code> \u4e2d\u52fe\u9009 <code>When (Thunderbird | Betterbird) is minimized, move it to the tray</code>.</li>\n<li>\u5b89\u88c5\u63d2\u4ef6 [Minimize on ...</li>\n</ol>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Typst/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/Typst/", "title": "Typst", "content_html": "<h1>Typst</h1>\n<p>[Typst] \u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u57fa\u4e8e\u6807\u8bb0\u7684\u6392\u7248\u7cfb\u7edf.</p>\n<p>\u4e0e LaTeX \u76f8\u6bd4:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u751f\u6001\u4e0d\u6210\u719f</strong>: Typst \u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u5305\u7d22\u5f15 [Typst Universe], \u4f46\u76ee\u524d\u5305\u7684\u6570\u91cf\u4ee5\u53ca\u5b8c\u6210\u5ea6\u90fd\u65e0\u6cd5\u4e0e LaTeX \u76f8\u6bd4.</li>\n<li>\u8bed\u6cd5\u66f4\u52a0\u7b80\u6d01\u6613\u7528.</li>\n<li><strong>\u65e0\u611f\u5305\u7ba1\u7406</strong>: Typst \u4f1a\u5728\u7f16\u8bd1\u65f6\u81ea\u52a8\u4e0b\u8f7d\u6240...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "date_published": "2025-09-28T17:56:52+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}]}